**Summary:** This documentation explains how to integrate Amplitude Session Replay with Segment analytics using three different destination modes: Amplitude Actions (using analytics_session_id cookie and Source Middleware), Amplitude Classic Device-mode (using amplitude-js SDK 5.2.2), and Amplitude Classic Cloud-mode (using Browser SDK as shell with sessionReplayPlugin).

